org.tapchain.core

インタフェース IBlueprint<ACTOR extends IPiece>

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    IActorBlueprint
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    ActorBlueprint, Blueprint, Blueprint.PieceBlueprintStatic, TapBlueprint

    public interface IBlueprint<ACTOR extends IPiece>
    Blueprint interface. Blueprint interface is the template of mutable objects. Manager can create mutable objects from Blueprint.

        Blueprint.TmpInstance<ACTOR> This()
